history.content:
Hey everyone,

Kind of late but I was wondering if you can suggest me, classes, to take in the Summer and upcoming fall.

I am currently enrolled in CS 161 and CS W169 for the summer session. My initial plan was to take CS 161 and one other Business Administration course. I have no internship experience and I was wondering if I should take W169 in the summer and take 161 in the fall or vice-versa. I am still applying for an internship but not sure if I will get a good offer so in this situation I am not sure what will be best to do. Any suggestion will be appreciated.

Also, I am not sure if the workload of CS 161 or 169, CS 189, COGSCI 131, and another Business Administration class is doable for the fall semester. I am graduating this fall and in total, I need 2 upper divs and 1 tech elective. I was wondering if you can suggest and share some of your experience and recommendation.

Thank you in advance.
history.subject: Suggestion for summer and Fall semester
